This paper is primarily focused on face recognition, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) category. The paper also discusses the use of a pretrained model and updating it, which involves machine learning techniques (cs.LG). Additionally, the paper deals with large datasets and graph construction, which could be relevant to multimedia (cs.MM) and information retrieval (cs.IR) sub-categories. Finally, the paper discusses the issue of labeling data, which could be relevant to the cryptography and security (cs.CR) sub-category.
